channel.title: Comments on: The Walkmen perform “In The New Year” on Conan

item.title: By: Drew
item.dc:creator: Drew
item.description:
Glad to see that the boys have ditched their Dockers on stage.
Khakis = No dice for a rock band.

item.title: By: Logan K. Young
item.dc:creator: Logan K. Young
item.description: man, late night has been incredible this week: these guys, andrew bird, M83. leithauser's voice reminds me of yours sometimes; i can see why you're a fan. the greatest thing is his ability to stay on pitch, even when he's clearly not in his most comfortable range. i was not all that into their previous efforts, but they really won me over with this record. great post!
